    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a masterpiece of automotive poetry. This isn't merely a vehicle; it\u2019s a portal to a more elegant era, where every mile is a brushstroke on the canvas of the open road. Draped in a finish that gleams like moonlight on still water, its silhouette commands the gaze of every passerby, whispering secrets of high-speed escapades and starlit drives. The engine doesn't just run; it breathes with a soulful, rhythmic cadence that invites you to leave the mundane behind. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of timeless craftsmanship, offering a tactile connection to a legacy of luxury. To own this car is to curate a piece of history\u2014a flawless companion for the discerning soul who seeks beauty in every turn.",
      "price": 46500.0,
